120
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:35,930
[Huang] [Qian] [Wei] [Feng]

121
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,480
Qian Xun from the sales department,

122
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,560
Huang Chengmin
from the finance department,

123
00:07:37,330 --> 00:07:42,300
[Huang] [Qian] [Wei] [Feng]

124
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:40,050
and Feng Kaixin from the HSKP Department,

125
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:42,070
