younger brother.

134
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:02,270
They have total control over
Purong Hotel's finances.

135
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,120
Xiang.

136
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,920
Touch any one of them,

137
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,140
