169
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:58,910
Yes.

170
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,460
I told you not to take on this mess.

171
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,360
Just let Kuanli

172
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,550
