176
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,750
I know Feng Kaixin.

177
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:16,070
He's just a good-for-nothing.

178
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:17,840
He only survives
because Wei Siyuan protects him.

179
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,790
[Huang] [Qian] [Wei] [Feng]

180
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:20,200
But Huang Chengmin is much more cunning.

181
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,980
You can tell from his accounts

182
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:23,080
that he

183
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,340
keeps a low profile,

184
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,080
and he's the sneaky type.

185
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,810
The head of the "iron triangle"

186
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,720
is Qian Xun.

187
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:31,270
In Purong Hotel, Wei Siyuan

188
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,730
