192
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:41,270
Watch out, he might
sabotage your performance.

193
00:09:41,270 --> 00:09:43,630
After all, he's in charge of
the sales department.

194
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:45,200
The economic lifeline of the whole hotel

195
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,600
