205
00:10:05,850 --> 00:10:07,840
That way, we can make sure
nothing goes wrong—

206
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,320
and it also sends them a message.

207
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,180
You focus on bringing in revenue,

208
00:10:11,330 --> 00:10:12,350
I'll help cut costs.

209
00:10:12,350 --> 00:10:13,270
You start auditing.

210
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,870
We'll hit from both sides.

211
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,360
I've caused you three a lot of trouble.

212
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,950
