223
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:09,630
You should take the initiative
to look after him.

224
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:15,830
Look after him?

225
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,080
Sure.

226
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:19,110
I'll "take good care" of him.

227
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,240
I promise

228
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,640
I'll kick him out
in less than three months.

229
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:30,180
I know that guy Ji's background.

230
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:33,240
Didn't he just study abroad
for a few years?

