Me?

280
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:06,430
Of course I'm upset!

281
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,530
Who doesn't know that woman

282
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,000
is Mr. Ji's favorite?

283
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:12,230
She gets all the spotlight?

284
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:13,390
It's gone too far.

285
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,270
The spotlight

286
00:14:15,380 --> 00:14:17,380
depends on how you let her take it.

287
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:19,670
If you want her to shine,

288
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:22,320
you let her shine the right way.

289
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:24,470
If you want her

290
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,510
to stumble,

291
00:14:27,330 --> 00:14:29,000
that's also an option.

292
00:14:29,620 --> 00:14:30,910
Right, Mr. Wei?

293
00:14:32,870 --> 00:14:34,030
What do you mean?

294
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:40,910
Between Xu Miyu and Ji Feng,

295
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:42,510
isn't there still you?

296
00:14:43,430 --> 00:14:46,230
You can just make some arrangements
in the middle,

297
00:14:47,930 --> 00:14:49,330
and set a trap for Xu Miyu.

298
00:14:50,010 --> 00:14:51,960
Will Ji Feng deal with it or not?

299
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,390
If he doesn't handle it,

300
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,510
he loses public support.

301
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:55,530
If he does handle it,

302
00:14:55,530 --> 00:14:56,870
he's already short-staffed—

303
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:58,060
he loses another person either way.

304
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:59,030
Brilliant.

305
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:02,210
You two are the brilliant ones.

306
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:06,510
Come on.

307
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,670
Stop drinking.

308
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,780
A toast to you two.

309
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:09,620
Bottoms up!

310
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,870
Drink less.

311
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,150
Think it over carefully.

312
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:15,510
Do some real work.

313
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,200
Kaixin.

314
00:15:23,990 --> 00:15:24,930
Ms. Xu,

315
00:15:25,510 --> 00:15:27,790
the executive floor
has been quite peaceful lately.

316
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:28,600
How is it?

317
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:30,400
Are you getting used to the work?

318
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,320
I'm trying to adapt.

319
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,030
Director,

320
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,440
I'll keep working hard.

321
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,150
Good.

322
00:15:35,190 --> 00:15:36,250
Very good.

323
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,390
Right now,

324
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:40,850
I have a good opportunity
for you to perform.

325
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,460
It's like this.

326
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:43,870
Next, our hotel

327
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:45,790
will be hosting an important VIP client.

328
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:46,550
Mr. Ji

329
00:15:46,550 --> 00:15:48,440
assigned this task to our HSKP Department.

330
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,670
Now I give it to you.

331
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,460
You should know

332
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:55,440
this is a rare opportunity
to prove yourself.

333
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:56,720
In our HSKP Department,

334
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:59,600
many forewomen
want to show their faces.

335
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,200
I have faith in you.

336
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,080
This

337
00:16:06,130 --> 00:16:07,660
is the customer's profile.

338
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:10,000
You must study it carefully
when you get back.

339
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,080
Prepare well,

340
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:13,370
and strive to make new contributions.

341
00:16:16,070 --> 00:16:17,200
Okay, Director.

342
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:20,350
[Customer Information of Purong Hotel]

343
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:22,310
What's wrong?

344
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:25,440
You look like you're not very willing.

345
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:27,290
No.

346
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:29,080
Thank you for your favor, Director.

347
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,030
Our executive floor

348
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:31,910
will definitely provide
good reception service.

349
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:32,430
Good.

350
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:33,850
Ms. Xu,

351
00:16:34,370 --> 00:16:36,480
I have high hopes for you.

352
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:38,820
Please make sure I won't

353
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:40,320
lose face in front of Mr. Ji.

354
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,030
Okay.

355
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,250
I will do my best.

356
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:43,910
Come on.

357
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,080
Go back and prepare well.

358
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,080
I'll be going now.

359
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:59,270
[Purong Hotel]

360
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,150
Mr. Qian,

361
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,670
here are the client profiles
you asked me to print.

362
00:17:00,670 --> 00:17:01,460
Please take a look.

363
00:17:01,460 --> 00:17:05,740
[Director's Office]

364
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:02,870
Keep them with you for now.

365
00:17:02,870 --> 00:17:04,680
But the notice says
this client is coming tomorrow.

366
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:06,210
How should we arrange this?

367
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,160
Well,

368
00:17:08,849 --> 00:17:10,579
ask everyone in the group chat.

369
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:13,450
Give these materials to
whoever is willing to go.

370
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:14,170
Okay.

371
00:17:18,990 --> 00:17:21,270
Notice: Colleagues, please check that

372
00:17:21,270 --> 00:17:22,680
the client's information is in the email.

373
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,310
Please actively participate

374
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:25,750
in the preparations for
hosting Libo Group's

375
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:27,000
APAC CBO,

376
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,569
Marcos Yang.

377
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:30,510
Thank you for your cooperation—

378
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:31,840
from sales department.

379
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:39,550
What I sent you

380
00:17:39,550 --> 00:17:40,920
is the renewal contract drafted by Purong.

381
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,580
Check it for any issues first.

382
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:46,320
I'll talk to Mr. Wei.

383
00:17:46,610 --> 00:17:48,470
I'll let you know when I have news.

384
00:17:50,980 --> 00:17:51,620
Honey,

385
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:54,510
don't be in a hurry to sign the contract.

386
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:55,310
What's wrong?

387
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:06,820
Purong Hotel is in a total mess right now.

388
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:08,320
Don't get involved.

389
00:18:08,790 --> 00:18:10,440
Changing ownership
is next year's business.

390
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,200
Besides,

391
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,600
Mr. Wei is not an outsider.

392
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:14,400
Let's just sign this year's contract.

393
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,830
That's not how it works.

394
00:18:16,290 --> 00:18:18,830
Whether Wei Siyuan's position
is secure or not,

395
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:20,070
it's hard to say.

396
00:18:20,620 --> 00:18:22,080
Anyway, just listen to me.

397
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:24,350
Sign it a couple of days later, okay?

398
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,070
Okay?

399
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:27,000
Okay.

400
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,460
I'll listen to you, honey.

401
00:18:31,310 --> 00:18:31,910
What is it?

402
00:18:31,980 --> 00:18:33,480
I have something good to show you.

403
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:34,410
What good thing?

404
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:37,540
[Yueting Real Estate:
Build A Home With Ingenuity]

405
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:41,070
Where we live now
is convenient and affordable.

406
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:42,270
Isn't it good enough?

407
00:18:42,850 --> 00:18:44,480
Look closely,

408
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:46,680
this is a school district house.

409
00:18:47,310 --> 00:18:48,920
The Experimental Primary School,

410
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:50,310
the Normal University
Affiliated Primary School,

411
00:18:50,310 --> 00:18:52,830
and several private primary schools
are all nearby.

412
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:55,260
I just passed by
when I met a client today,

413
00:18:55,350 --> 00:18:57,180
and saw many people rushing to buy it.

414
00:18:57,180 --> 00:18:58,370
Look at this floor plan.

415
00:18:58,370 --> 00:18:59,900
[The highlight of the household]

416
00:18:58,750 --> 00:19:00,790
Every room faces south.

417
00:19:01,160 --> 00:19:02,590
Where else can you
find a floor plan like this?

418
00:19:02,590 --> 00:19:03,790
After the child is born,

419
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:06,410
whether a nanny or our mom comes to help,

420
00:19:06,550 --> 00:19:08,240
don't they need a nice place to stay?

421
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,640
Right, that makes sense.

422
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:12,000
But the problem
is the child hasn't been born yet.

423
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,590
It's too early for school.

424
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:16,270
Now to go to primary school,

425
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:18,870
you need 5 years of school district house
qualification in advance.

426
00:19:18,870 --> 00:19:20,310
You still think it's too early?

427
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:21,620
You silly dad.

428
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:23,500
Let's wait until I'm done with
this busy period.

429
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:24,260
No.

430
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:26,400
We have to go house hunting this weekend.

431
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,860
Otherwise, this floor plan
will be sold out.

432
00:19:28,890 --> 00:19:29,870
Honey,

433
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:32,310
I've been really busy at work lately.

434
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:38,280
Which is more important,
the baby or the company?

435
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,270
Which is more important,
the baby or the company?

436
00:19:41,270 --> 00:19:42,800
The baby is more important.

437
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:47,030
Let's go take a look this weekend.

438
00:20:10,810 --> 00:20:12,890
[Health condition]
[Psychology health attention]

439
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:23,720
Mr. Ji.

440
00:20:24,490 --> 00:20:26,200
How are you doing with the materials?

441
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,110
Almost done.

442
00:20:27,110 --> 00:20:28,710
I'll review them twice more.

443
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,550
Mr. Yang

444
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:31,920
is Spanish-Chinese.

445
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:34,720
He has a deep affection
for Chinese culture.

446
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:36,550
He travels around the world all year round

447
00:20:36,550 --> 00:20:38,810
and has stayed in various luxury hotels.

448
00:20:39,110 --> 00:20:40,680
This time he comes to Shanghai

449
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:42,340
and chooses our Purong Hotel.

450
00:20:42,460 --> 00:20:43,650
He has high expectations

451
00:20:43,650 --> 00:20:44,960
for this stay.

452
00:20:44,990 --> 00:20:46,950
Details are your strong suit.

453
00:20:46,970 --> 00:20:48,300
I'll leave this to you.

454
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,280
I understand, Mr. Ji.

455
00:20:49,290 --> 00:20:55,720
[Receptionist]

456
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:50,860
Okay.

457
00:20:54,790 --> 00:20:56,310
You're the only one here today?

458
00:20:56,310 --> 00:20:57,570
I'm on the night shift.

459
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:58,680
Find someone

460
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:00,740
to cover your shift and get some rest.

461
00:21:00,810 --> 00:21:02,170
I don't want you

462
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:03,510
to look sleep-deprived tomorrow

463
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:04,710
when receiving VIPs.

464
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:05,670
Okay.

465
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:06,350
Okay.

466
00:21:07,090 --> 00:21:08,500
[Receptionist]

467
00:21:13,230 --> 00:21:13,880
Mr. Ji,

468
00:21:14,310 --> 00:21:15,160
don't worry.

469
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:17,480
Tomorrow, the executive floor
will definitely

470
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:19,030
use our fullest enthusiasm,

471
00:21:19,030 --> 00:21:19,910
overcome all difficulties,

472
00:21:19,910 --> 00:21:21,710
and help you win this big client.

473
00:21:24,070 --> 00:21:24,790
Okay.

474
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:35,730
[Purong Hotel]

475
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:35,510
Hello, Mr. Ji.

476
00:21:35,510 --> 00:21:36,110
Hello.

477
00:21:47,340 --> 00:21:48,270
Morning, Mr. Ji.

478
00:21:53,110 --> 00:21:54,310
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

479
00:21:55,830 --> 00:21:57,760
I'm Lu Zhenzhen from the sales department.

480
00:21:57,760 --> 00:21:58,820
Do you remember me?

481
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:02,130
My mother-in-law
just had her 60th birthday last month.

482
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:02,760
Of course.

483
00:22:03,110 --> 00:22:04,510
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

484
00:22:04,660 --> 00:22:06,350
I just transferred to
the sales department.

485
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:08,050
Please take care of me, Mr. Ji.

486
00:22:10,070 --> 00:22:11,110
Hello, Ms. Xu.

487
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:15,410
Mr. Ji,

488
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:16,310
I won't let

489
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:18,910
any personal feelings interfere with
my work.

490
00:22:26,310 --> 00:22:27,160
Oh my god.

491
00:22:27,310 --> 00:22:29,350
The wife and the mistress
are in the same frame.

492
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:30,680
Are they going to fight?

493
00:22:49,370 --> 00:22:50,290
Marcos,

494
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:53,290
I'm great to see you in Shanghai.

495
00:22:53,290 --> 00:22:54,220
Long time no see.

496
00:22:55,260 --> 00:22:56,460
Hello, I am Zhen,

497
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:59,480
the sales representative
from Purong Hotel.

498
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:01,030
After the long journey,

499
00:23:01,050 --> 00:23:05,440
would you prefer to take a rest
or grab something to eat first?

500
00:23:05,470 --> 00:23:06,670
I'll rest first.

501
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:11,020
Welcome, Mr. Marcos.

502
00:23:11,040 --> 00:23:12,310
I'll take you to your room.

503
00:23:12,310 --> 00:23:13,310
This way, please.

504
00:23:13,550 --> 00:23:14,220
Thank you.

505
00:23:26,570 --> 00:23:28,170
Welcome.

506
00:23:28,650 --> 00:23:31,020
Good morning, Mr. Yang.

507
00:23:31,310 --> 00:23:34,830
I'm the director of the rooms.

508
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:38,280
My name is Feng Kaixin.

509
00:23:40,070 --> 00:23:41,030
Hello, Mr. Feng.

510
00:23:41,940 --> 00:23:43,440
Mr. Yang, your Chinese is so good.

511
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,130
Great.

512
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:46,510
Mr. Yang, please come in.

513
00:23:57,710 --> 00:23:58,470
Excuse me.

514
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:09,350
Marcos,

515
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:11,640
after such a long flight,

516
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:12,510
