517
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:14,840
You can go to the restaurant
for some food.

518
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,310
No need to be so complicated.

519
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:18,770
I'll just grab a bite here.

520
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:22,040
There are ready-made sandwiches
in the Executive Lounge.

521
00:24:22,040 --> 00:24:23,190
Cold food is bad for the stomach.

522
00:24:23,190 --> 00:24:24,550
Marcos has a weak stomach.

523
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:26,750
The Executive Lounge can make hot food.

524
00:24:27,270 --> 00:24:28,070
How long will it take?

525
00:24:28,070 --> 00:24:28,720
Anytime.

526
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:30,450
Serve the dishes immediately.

527
00:24:54,690 --> 00:24:55,530
Master Yue,

528
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:56,750
did anyone else give you

529
00:24:56,750 --> 00:24:58,000
