530
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:58,640
No.

531
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,090
Okay, thank you.

532
00:25:28,110 --> 00:25:28,960
Your business banquet

533
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:31,890
is actually very suitable
to be held at Purong Hotel.

534
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:35,880
I think your hotel
is indeed quite tasteful.

535
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,790
It's just that the other company
has already

536
00:25:37,790 --> 00:25:39,310
booked a restaurant in advance.

537
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:41,160
It's okay. There will be
other opportunities in the future.

538
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:41,790
It's a pity.

539
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:43,920
There will be opportunities anytime.

540
00:25:44,510 --> 00:25:45,350
Ms. Xu.

541
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,750
This salad is a bit too much.

542
00:25:48,750 --> 00:25:50,280
I'll portion it out for you.

543
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:51,150
Thank you.

544
00:25:58,350 --> 00:25:59,070
Thank you.

545
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:01,160
Swap out the egg and mayonnaise,

546
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:02,720
and replace them with
Japanese roasted sesame dressing

547
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:03,610
and chicken breast.

548
00:26:03,610 --> 00:26:04,590
Halve the portion.

549
00:26:04,590 --> 00:26:05,160
Make it fast.

550
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:05,790
Okay.

551
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:10,400
Thank you.

552
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:21,590
I don't mean to look down on you.

553
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:24,140
At this level, you're still managing to

554
00:26:24,140 --> 00:26:26,600
