on the executive floor?

555
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:35,160
We'd hate to disturb you.

556
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:36,090
Have a good rest.

557
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,160
Ms. Xu,

558
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:55,650
your explanation?

559
00:26:55,790 --> 00:26:56,790
I am sorry, Mr. Ji.

560
00:26:57,270 --> 00:26:59,800
The person you should
apologize to is Marcos.

561
00:27:02,070 --> 00:27:03,350
But on my documents...

562
00:27:03,370 --> 00:27:04,550
Ms. Xu,

563
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:07,550
I told you again and again yesterday

564
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,920
and emphasized

565
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,550
the importance of this task.

566
00:27:10,550 --> 00:27:12,350
How could you still make
such an amateur mistake?

567
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:14,610
I handed such an important client to you.

568
00:27:14,630 --> 00:27:16,480
It is clearly written in the documents

569
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:18,310
that Marcos is allergic to pollen

570
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:19,750
and eggs.

571
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:21,920
You didn't even look at
such important information.

572
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:23,830
Do you have any sense of
responsibility for your work?

573
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:25,140
You brought shame to our executive floor,

574
00:27:25,140 --> 00:27:25,750
no,

575
00:27:25,780 --> 00:27:28,220
the entire HSKP Department.

576
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:30,310
Mr. Feng, the documents
you gave me clearly...

577
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:31,630
You're still explaining, huh?

578
00:27:31,630 --> 00:27:32,290
Look at you,

579
00:27:32,490 --> 00:27:33,720
still trying to pass the buck to me.

580
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:34,850
If it weren't for me

581
00:27:34,870 --> 00:27:37,180
and Mr. Ji taking charge
on the spot today,

582
00:27:37,180 --> 00:27:40,380
who knows how much loss the hotel
would have suffered?

583
00:27:40,410 --> 00:27:41,760
Look at your working attitude

584
00:27:41,760 --> 00:27:42,520
and level.

585
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:45,680
Do you still deserve to be
an executive floor forewoman?

586
00:27:46,190 --> 00:27:47,080
Ms. Xu,

587
00:27:47,560 --> 00:27:48,780
can you handle it well?

588
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:49,430
I can.

589
00:27:49,970 --> 00:27:51,570
I'll trust you one more time.

590
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:56,940
Just let it go?

591
00:28:04,070 --> 00:28:04,790
Ms. Xu,

592
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:06,670
Mr. Ji wants to see you in his office.

593
00:28:06,670 --> 00:28:07,530
I was just heading there.

594
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:08,990
[Receptionist]

595
00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:11,940
Come in.

596
00:28:13,530 --> 00:28:14,340
Mr. Ji,

597
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,510
I've read this document over ten times,

598
00:28:17,510 --> 00:28:18,640
and I've memorized it.

599
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:19,720
It really doesn't mention

600
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:21,310
Marcos' food allergies.

601
00:28:24,910 --> 00:28:25,670
Here.

602
00:28:29,580 --> 00:28:31,380
[Allergies: allergic to pollen and eggs.]

603
00:28:34,590 --> 00:28:35,660
[Professional Background]

604
00:28:35,110 --> 00:28:35,720
Wait,

605
00:28:36,070 --> 00:28:37,660
this is not my file.

606
00:28:37,790 --> 00:28:38,510
I highlighted my copy of the materials

607
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:40,310
with a marker.

608
00:28:44,690 --> 00:28:48,010
[Health status] [Mental health concerns]

609
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:49,480
Look.

610
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:51,480
Fortunately, I have a photo.

611
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:53,220
It was marked with a highlighter.

612
00:28:52,620 --> 00:28:53,740
[Health status]

613
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:55,400
Not bad.

614
00:28:55,510 --> 00:28:56,710
You reacted quickly.

615
00:28:58,110 --> 00:29:00,070
I know this was not your fault.

616
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:01,570
I called you here

617
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,110
to give you a new one.

618
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:04,780
Then just now...

619
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:06,410
You were eager to prove yourself,

620
00:29:06,410 --> 00:29:08,410
and I wanted to see what you could do.

621
00:29:08,550 --> 00:29:09,470
Mr. Ji.

622
00:29:09,510 --> 00:29:09,980
All right.

623
00:29:09,980 --> 00:29:11,640
That's the end of this matter.

624
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:14,830
It's safer if you use my version.

625
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:17,030
For all future reception work,

626
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:18,490
you report directly to me.

627
00:29:18,550 --> 00:29:19,320
Understood?

628
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:22,160
Understood.

629
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:24,350
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

630
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:47,540
Mr. Marcos,

631
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:48,960
I know that Libo Group

632
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,540
is known globally for its long-termism.

633
00:29:51,750 --> 00:29:54,350
The acquisition of Taisheng Metropolis
seven years ago

634
00:29:54,350 --> 00:29:56,240
is unsurpassed among

635
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:58,100
global construction companies.

636
00:29:58,160 --> 00:30:00,370
Has your hotel cooperated with Libo?

637
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:01,190
Of course.

638
00:30:01,340 --> 00:30:03,160
Our hotel hosted the annual meeting

639
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:03,960
of Libo Group's

640
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:06,640
branch in Shanghai, China last year.

641
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,790
We are also negotiating

642
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:10,750
with Libo Group's partner,
Shenjiang Industry,

643
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:12,010
on some projects.

644
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:13,180
Sorry,

645
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:15,480
I'm late.

646
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:17,050
Sorry to keep you waiting.

647
00:30:17,750 --> 00:30:18,360
How is it?

648
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:20,570
Are you used to the food?

649
00:30:20,620 --> 00:30:21,750
This meat is not bad.

650
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,140
It's especially tender
when I bite into it.

651
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:24,070
I really like it.

652
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:27,980
This is our hotel's signature dish.

653
00:30:28,540 --> 00:30:31,270
The veal shank is very delicious.

654
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:34,030
It was carefully prepared for you

655
00:30:34,030 --> 00:30:35,630
by a chef in our kitchen who specializes

656
00:30:35,630 --> 00:30:36,930
in Mediterranean cuisine.

657
00:30:36,930 --> 00:30:37,890
So thoughtful.

658
00:30:40,350 --> 00:30:41,280
Braised prawns.

659
00:30:42,260 --> 00:30:42,980
Try it.

660
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:51,110
The flavor is quite rich.

661
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:54,000
How was it made?

662
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:55,780
It

663
00:30:57,170 --> 00:30:58,100
is made by our...

664
00:30:58,760 --> 00:31:00,040
This cuisine

665
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:01,670
mainly depends on the sauce.

666
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:03,640
In most places, the sauce

667
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:06,380
is made by mixing store-bought ketchup.

668
00:31:06,410 --> 00:31:08,480
But in our kitchen, the sauce is made

669
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:10,310
by simmering wild mushroom broth together

670
00:31:10,310 --> 00:31:12,590
with fresh tomatoes,

671
00:31:12,590 --> 00:31:14,730
so it has a very seasonal flavor.

672
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:17,600
So did you arrange

673
00:31:18,910 --> 00:31:20,340
these dishes?

674
00:31:20,390 --> 00:31:23,550
I learned that you prefer Chinese cuisine,

675
00:31:23,770 --> 00:31:25,960
and you also like
various kinds of seafood.

676
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:27,350
So for tonight's menu,

677
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:30,400
most of it is Chinese-style seafood.

678
00:31:34,670 --> 00:31:35,500
Thank you.

679
00:31:35,800 --> 00:31:36,990
I'm glad you like it.

680
00:31:37,550 --> 00:31:38,380
I love it.

681
00:31:39,410 --> 00:31:40,410
And thank you too.

682
00:31:40,570 --> 00:31:42,030
You are all like my family.

683
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:44,160
You know me very well.

684
00:31:44,550 --> 00:31:45,350
Right, Kenny?

685
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:46,790
Of course.

686
00:31:47,430 --> 00:31:49,190
The service staff you trained

687
00:31:49,210 --> 00:31:51,350
have never disappointed me.

688
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:53,240
You're flattering us.

689
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:53,830
Don't be.

690
00:31:53,830 --> 00:31:54,550
Come.

691
00:31:54,650 --> 00:31:55,590
Cheers.

692
00:31:55,620 --> 00:31:57,550
It's really great.

693
00:31:58,050 --> 00:31:59,250
As long as you like it.

694
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:14,410
[Receipt]

695
00:32:14,410 --> 00:32:16,030
[Shang PIN JIN HUO JI LU BIAO]

696
00:32:18,470 --> 00:32:19,070
Who is it?

697
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,200
Xue Rui!

698
00:32:20,990 --> 00:32:21,530
Xue...

699
00:32:21,970 --> 00:32:22,830
Mr. Xue?

700
00:32:22,210 --> 00:32:24,120
[Shang PIN JIN HUO JI LU BIAO] [Receipt]

701
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,070
Wait a moment!

702
00:32:27,910 --> 00:32:28,400
Coming.

703
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:29,640
Coming.

704
00:32:32,090 --> 00:32:32,860
Mr. Chen.

705
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:34,110
Why is your door locked?

706
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:34,960
What are you hiding?

707
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,750
Mr. Xue, why are you here?

708
00:32:36,990 --> 00:32:38,610
It's a bit chaotic.

709
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:39,670
It will

710
00:32:39,830 --> 00:32:41,120
ruin

711
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:42,240
your suit.

712
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:44,240
Are you treating me like a stranger?

713
00:32:44,830 --> 00:32:45,960
It's a work uniform.

714
00:32:46,300 --> 00:32:47,160
Did you forget?

715
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,800
We used to come here
at the end of every month

716
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:50,520
to settle accounts.

717
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:51,510
Right.

718
00:32:51,870 --> 00:32:55,000
You were in charge of
the purchasing accounts back then.

719
00:32:57,030 --> 00:32:58,160
This place is great.

720
00:32:58,590 --> 00:32:59,970
This is the granary of Purong Hotel.

721
00:32:59,970 --> 00:33:01,160
It is a treasured place.

722
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,760
I want to live here every day.

723
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:04,450
How is it going?

724
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:05,450
Are you busy?

725
00:33:05,660 --> 00:33:06,640
Business is okay.

726
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,790
We have a few tables for lunch.

727
00:33:07,790 --> 00:33:08,380
But,

728
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,010
they are all regular customers.

729
00:33:10,010 --> 00:33:10,910
No new ones.

730
00:33:12,790 --> 00:33:15,120
How much revenue do you make during lunch?

731
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:22,160
Brother Chen,

732
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:24,550
can you let me see your purchase orders?

733
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,160
I'm afraid not.

734
00:33:27,780 --> 00:33:28,910
Chef Jia is not here.

735
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:30,350
I can't make the call.

736
00:33:30,350 --> 00:33:31,400
Come on.

737
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:34,070
You are the manager
of the purchasing department.

738
00:33:34,070 --> 00:33:35,510
You can't even make this call?

739
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:37,070
What purchasing department manager?

740
00:33:37,070 --> 00:33:38,880
I'm just a grocery shopper.

741
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:42,400
Okay.

742
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:43,500
I won't make things difficult for you.

743
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:44,240
Look,

744
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,590
when Chef Jia comes back,

745
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:47,880
ask him to prepare the purchase order

746
00:33:47,880 --> 00:33:49,280
and hand it in to me today.

747
00:33:49,650 --> 00:33:50,070
No.

748
00:33:50,090 --> 00:33:51,020
This won't do.

749
00:33:52,310 --> 00:33:52,880
Brother,

750
00:33:53,450 --> 00:33:54,830
let me be honest with you.

751
00:33:54,830 --> 00:33:56,340
The new boss

752
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:59,750
has been looking at
the Chinese restaurant's bills lately.

753
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:01,280
They are really rushing me.

754
00:34:01,490 --> 00:34:02,620
Do me a favor.

755
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:03,500
After Chef Jia comes back,

756
00:34:03,500 --> 00:34:05,560
have him prepare it and hand it over to me

757
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:06,760
so I can report back

758
00:34:08,080 --> 00:34:08,969
and get through this.

759
00:34:08,969 --> 00:34:09,739
I see.

760
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:12,150
All right.

761
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:13,480
I will definitely tell him.

762
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,630
Okay, thanks.

763
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:15,230
I'll let you get back to work.

764
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:16,030
It's nothing.

765
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:16,949
The cup.

766
00:34:17,190 --> 00:34:17,790
Thank you.

767
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:19,040
Okay, take care.

768
00:34:19,250 --> 00:34:19,810
Bye.

769
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:20,590
Bye.

770
00:34:43,040 --> 00:34:43,780
How did it go?

771
00:34:45,699 --> 00:34:46,630
I'm already this old,

772
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:47,710
and I still have to
play spy games with you.

773
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:49,510
Good thing I have strong nerves.

774
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:52,900
I said everything you told me to say.

775
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:54,199
But your goal

776
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:56,510
definitely isn't
just the purchase order, right?

777
00:34:56,510 --> 00:34:57,710
You know me best, Rui.

778
00:34:59,200 --> 00:35:01,600
Are you still not going to
tell me your plan?

779
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:07,480
Here.

780
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:14,570
[Personnel Registration
Form of Purong Hotel]

781
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,280
Jia Shikun

782
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:15,940
claims to be a disciple
of Huaiyang cuisine master Gu Shanghong.

783
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:15,780
[Name: Jia Shikun]

784
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:18,230
Relying on his signature dish—
salted pork rib soup with bamboo shoots—

785
00:35:18,230 --> 00:35:20,000
said to be a top specialty in Shanghai,

786
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:20,800
he has been secretly taking advantage of

787
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:23,730
the hotel for years,
and no one has dared to touch him.

788
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:26,980
To solve the problem
of our Chinese restaurant,

789
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:28,330
he must be eliminated.

790
00:35:29,670 --> 00:35:31,320
I know about Jia Shikun's problem.

791
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,520
But if you touch him,

792
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:34,230
the board won't agree.

793
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,440
So I want him to leave by himself.

794
00:35:38,790 --> 00:35:41,050
How are you so sure
he'll leave on his own?

795
00:35:41,230 --> 00:35:43,070
He's hot-tempered

796
00:35:43,190 --> 00:35:44,480
and cares most about his reputation.

797
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,960
Even Wei Siyuan
takes a detour when he sees him.

798
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:48,510
A newly appointed manager,

799
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:51,190
recklessly trying to use him as an example

800
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:53,070
and making him hand over
the account books...

801
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:55,150
Do you think he'll be furious

802
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:57,150
and try to assert dominance over me?

803
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:59,510
That's all your guess.

804
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,980
I asked a headhunter I know.

805
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:04,630
There are quite a few hotels
trying to recruit him this month,

806
00:36:04,630 --> 00:36:06,880
including Kuanli Hotel.

807
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,920
I'm just giving him a little push.

808
00:36:17,870 --> 00:36:19,190
Be quick about it!

809
00:36:20,070 --> 00:36:20,670
Chef!

810
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:21,870
You're finally here.

811
00:36:22,030 --> 00:36:24,160
I've been looking for you everywhere.

812
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:31,290
You cut it so big?

813
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,590
You want to choke someone?

814
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:33,150
Recut it!

815
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:37,590
What is it? Speak.

816
00:36:37,640 --> 00:36:38,320
Speak.

817
00:36:39,190 --> 00:36:41,190
The higher-ups are investigating.

818
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:42,690
The higher-ups?

819
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:43,510
Yes.

820
00:36:46,630 --> 00:36:47,850
Is it the guy surnamed Ji?

821
00:36:47,850 --> 00:36:48,670
Yes.

822
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,300
The new boss is taking office

823
00:36:52,300 --> 00:36:54,500
and throwing his weight around my turf?

824
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,590
They're forcing us
to hand in the list today.

825
00:36:57,590 --> 00:36:59,510
Why don't we just fool them a bit

826
00:36:59,510 --> 00:37:00,240
and let it go?

827
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:01,980
If you want to play,

828
00:37:02,110 --> 00:37:03,190
go play with him.

829
00:37:03,350 --> 00:37:04,340
I won't.

830
00:37:05,520 --> 00:37:06,920
Chef, don't be like this.

831
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:08,840
Don't talk to me, I quit.

832
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:09,480
Listen to me.

833
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:11,550
You suppress this matter first.

834
00:37:11,550 --> 00:37:13,230
We will always have a way out later.

835
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:14,020
Take what?

836
00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:14,840
What do we do?

837
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:15,590
-What should I tell him?
-Calm down.

838
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:16,070
I'll talk to him.

839
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:16,630
I will tell him.

840
00:37:16,630 --> 00:37:17,440
Don't be in a rush to leave.

841
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:17,960
Well..

842
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:18,820
Right, just...

843
00:37:20,580 --> 00:37:21,780
Good for you.

844
00:37:22,070 --> 00:37:23,380
You did so much on your own,

845
00:37:23,380 --> 00:37:24,960
and didn't tell me anything.

846
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:25,760
If I had told you,

847
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:27,190
Rui, would you still have

848
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:30,590
such excellent acting skills
in the purchasing department?

849
00:37:33,120 --> 00:37:36,480
Do you have a suitable chef?

850
00:37:38,250 --> 00:37:40,310
I have someone I'd like to try hiring.

851
00:37:48,110 --> 00:37:49,440
At Duan Aoxiang's banquet,

852
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:50,820
[Personnel Registration
Form of Purong Hotel]

853
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:50,640
I saw her creativity.

854
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:51,750
She graduated
from Le Cordon Bleu in France.

855
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,430
[Name: Li Qiaoqi]

856
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:53,070
She has ideas and she's capable.

857
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:56,530
And I heard she has a particularly
good relationship with you.

858
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:01,070
Yes.

859
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:02,320
I know her quite well.

860
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:03,880
She's straightforward

861
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:05,030
and a doer.

862
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:07,070
She can definitely be trusted.

863
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:08,380
Once Jia Shikun leaves,

864
00:38:08,380 --> 00:38:10,150
he will definitely
take his kitchen staff with him.

865
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:11,710
As long as we give her more time

866
00:38:11,710 --> 00:38:12,550
and trust her,

867
00:38:12,710 --> 00:38:14,570
