868
00:38:14,710 --> 00:38:15,480
In that case,

869
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,210
we...

870
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:17,760
Come in.

871
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:20,320
Mr. Ji, Director Lu is...

872
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:21,240
Mr. Ji,

873
00:38:23,070 --> 00:38:24,350
at 6:30 tonight,

874
00:38:24,550 --> 00:38:26,030
Mr. Marcos' business banquet

875
00:38:26,030 --> 00:38:28,000
will be changed to
the small banquet hall in our hotel.

876
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:28,350
[Banquet Hall Application]

877
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:28,670
A total of five tables.

878
00:38:28,670 --> 00:38:29,530
Please sign it.

879
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:31,440
Are you sure?

880
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:32,000
I'm sure.

881
00:38:32,260 --> 00:38:33,630
It took me a whole day

882
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:35,550
to finally convince Mr. Marcos

883
00:38:35,550 --> 00:38:37,150
to move the banquet to our hotel.

884
00:38:35,830 --> 00:38:37,200
[Banquet Hall Application]
[General Manager's Approval: Approved]

885
00:38:37,150 --> 00:38:38,960
There will be many big shots tonight.

886
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:40,190
Top executives from
the construction, mining,

887
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:40,740
[Banquet invitation request department:
Sales Department]
[General Manager: Ji Feng]

888
00:38:40,190 --> 00:38:42,590
and real estate industries will be here.

889
00:38:42,590 --> 00:38:43,760
This is a very rare

890
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:44,920
promotional opportunity for us.

891
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,760
You are in charge of this banquet.

892
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:48,260
Report to me if anything comes up.

893
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:48,900
Rui.

894
00:38:52,550 --> 00:38:54,360
Director Lu picked a great time to come.

895
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:56,280
Jia Shikun might not have left today.

896
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:58,300
With such a good chance to set me up,

897
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:00,080
