898
00:39:00,080 --> 00:39:00,830
What should we do then?

899
00:39:00,830 --> 00:39:02,150
Should we ask HR?

900
00:39:02,190 --> 00:39:04,110
Didn't you say we should
let Li Qiaoqi have a try?

901
00:39:04,110 --> 00:39:05,150
Now is the chance.

902
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:07,350
Let's see if she can seize
the opportunity.

903
00:39:07,350 --> 00:39:08,340
She can do it.

904
00:39:07,690 --> 00:39:10,740
[Dinner menu] [Cold dishes] [Hot dishes]
[Staple food][Soup]

905
00:39:13,290 --> 00:39:15,390
How long does it take
to cook a five-table dinner?

906
00:39:15,390 --> 00:39:16,790
It's not a matter of time.

907
00:39:17,190 --> 00:39:18,070
You saw it too.

908
00:39:18,070 --> 00:39:20,310
Chef Jia took more than
half of the kitchen staff away.

909
00:39:20,310 --> 00:39:21,240
I need manpower.

910
00:39:21,850 --> 00:39:22,760
How many do you need?

911
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,780
I want three Sous Chefs,

912
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:24,840
and a dessert chef.

913
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:26,600
I can't give you three.

914
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:27,610
I'll give you one first,

915
00:39:27,610 --> 00:39:30,760
